  "title": "EarthMobs",
  "description": "bring back to the Minecraft Earth Mobs with own twist on gameplay!",
  "body": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/913527/description_221da422-5d08-4876-8283-717f37df1e99.png\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #fff;\">Remember the mobs from&nbsp;<strong>Minecraft Earth</strong>? Well they're back!<br>In this mod, we have added an array of mobs you might've seen from Minecraft Earth. From the Muddiest Pigs to the Jolliest Llamas, &amp; new dangers like the climbing Boulderer &amp; overwhelming Viler Witches. You can find all these mobs scattered across the Overworld!<br>Most of the ideas &amp; concepts originated by Mojang Studios, but brought to the base game by us!&nbsp;<em>With some tweaks to integrate with vanilla gameplay &amp; style.</em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\">(Requires:&nbsp;<a style=\"color: #fff;\" href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/bagus-lib\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bagus Lib</a>)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; color: #f00;\"><strong>&nbsp;!Backports &amp; Fabric ports are not planned!</strong></span></p></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>:Credits:</strong></span><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BL9gVVb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"45\" height=\"45\">Evo_934</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BL9gVVb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"45\" height=\"45\"></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">(Lead artist)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BL9gVVb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"45\" height=\"45\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">baguchi</span><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BL9gVVb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"45\" height=\"45\"></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">(Lead coder)</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BL9gVVb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"45\" height=\"45\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Farcr &amp; MCVinnyq</span></strong><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BL9gVVb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"45\" height=\"45\"></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">(Former artists and owner)</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Special Thanks</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">elliebear</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;azzy</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Achefslife</span></p>",
